| Type       | Pattern                | Example                                |
| ---------- | ---------------------- | -------------------------------------- |
| Module     | `<Feature>Module`      | `FeatureModule`                        |
| Controller | `<Feature>Controller`  | `FeatureController`                    |
| Service    | `<Feature>Service`     | `FeatureService`                       |
